'''第64届[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]'''于2011年5月11日至5月22日在[[法国|法国]][[戛纳|戛纳]]举办<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en.html |title=Festival de Cannes 2011 |accessdate=2011-01-01 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408003127/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[泰伦斯·马力克|泰伦斯·马力克]]执导的影片《[[生命樹_(電影)|生命樹]]》摘得最高荣誉[[金棕榈奖|金棕榈奖]]。美国演员[[罗伯特·德尼罗|罗伯特·德尼罗]]為正式競賽項目的评审团主席<ref>{{Cite web|last1=Hopewell|first1=John|last2=Keslassy|first2=Elsa|date=2011-01-06|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118029833?refCatId=13|title=Robert De Niro to head Cannes jury|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2011-01-06|archive-date=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107084733/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118029833?refCatId=13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2011-01-06|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12128925|title=Robert De Niro to head Cannes Film Festival jury|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-01-06|archive-date=2011-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110107050626/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12128925|dead-url=no}}</ref>，開幕片為[[伍迪·艾倫|伍迪·艾倫]]執導的《[[午夜巴黎|午夜巴黎]]》。

